name: John Wick Chapter 4
intro: With the price on his head ever increasing, legendary hit man John Wick takes his fight against the High Table global as he seeks out the most powerful players in the underworld, from New York to Paris to Japan to Berlin.

name: Jurassic World
intro: Four years after the destruction of Isla Nublar, dinosaurs now live and hunt alongside humans all over the world. This fragile balance will reshape the future and determine, once and for all, whether human beings are to remain the apex predators on a planet they now share with history's most fearsome creatures.

name: The Boys
intro: Superheroes are often as popular as celebrities, as influential as politicians, and sometimes even as revered as gods.

name: Money Heist
intro: “Money Heist” is a thrilling action series that follows a group of robbers as they plan and execute heists on the Royal Mint of Spain. With high stakes, intricate plans, and unexpected twists, this show keeps viewers on the edge of their seats.

name: Ant-Man and The Wasp Quantumania
intro: Ant-Man and The Wasp Quantumania” continues the adventures of Scott Lang (Ant-Man) and Hope van Dyne (The Wasp) as they navigate the quantum realm. With humor, action, and mind-bending science, this film explores the hidden dimensions of the Marvel Cinematic Universe.

name: Avengers: Infinity War
intro: The Avengers must stop Thanos, an intergalactic warlord, from getting his hands on all the infinity stones. However, Thanos is prepared to go to any lengths to carry out his insane plan.

name: Moon Knight
intro: Steven Grant and mercenary Marc Spector investigate the mysteries of the Egyptian gods from inside the same body.

name: Kota Factory
intro: Like many students from across India, Vaibhav comes to Kota to prepare for JEE and NEET. Along with his friends, he navigates campus life and works hard to get into IIT.

name: Collage Romance
intro: Three friends, Karan, Trippy and Naira, are inseparable and begin their college life together. However, when they fall in love, they face challenges in their romantic lives.

name: Thor Love Of Thunder
intro: Thor embarks on a journey unlike anything he's ever faced -- a quest for inner peace. However, his retirement gets interrupted by Gorr the God Butcher, a galactic killer who seeks the extinction of the gods. To combat the threat, Thor enlists the help of King Valkyrie, Korg and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster, who -- to his surprise -- inexplicably wields his magical hammer. Together, they set out on a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher's vengeance.

name: Uncharted
intro: Victor Sullivan recruits Nathan Drake to help him find the lost fortune of Ferdinand Magellan. However, they face competition from Santiago Moncada, who believes that the treasure belongs to him.

name: Top Gun
intro: Thirty years of service leads Maverick to train a group of elite TOPGUN graduates to prepare for a high-profile mission while Maverick battles his past demons.

name: Eternals
intro: The Eternals, a race of immortal beings with superhuman powers who have secretly lived on Earth for thousands of years, reunite to battle the evil Deviants.

name: Spider Man
intro: Spider-Man seeks the help of Doctor Strange to forget his exposed secret identity as Peter Parker. However, Strange's spell goes horribly wrong, leading to unwanted guests entering their universe.
